        <h1>Does Predestination Make God the Author of Sin?</h1>

        <p class="subtitle">The most emotionally charged objection to Reformed theology — and one that Scripture itself anticipates and answers.</p>
    </section>


        <nav class="section-nav" role="navigation" aria-label="Section navigation">
